column5: I am going to be arriving in Selkirk Monday morning, and I am concerned that I wont be able to find a place to buy Fishing liscenses, since it is thanksgiving up there on monday. Anyone know if the main baitshop is open in selkirk that day, or can anyone tell me where else I could go in Winnipeg or somewhere close to selkirk, if they are not open THanks for the help
